  "full_text": "An update for java-17-openjdk is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe RHEL 9.7 GA release was prepared with the most recent release of OpenJDK 17 at that time, which was OpenJDK 17.0.16, released on July 15 2025.  OpenJDK 17.0.17 was subsequently released on October 21 2025, with existing RHEL 9 releases (9.0, 9.2, 9.4 and 9.6) being updated at that time.  This update now brings OpenJDK 17.0.17 to RHEL 9.7.For more information about the changes in OpenJDK 17.0.17, see the release notes listed in the References section."
